Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.41,0:03:51.74,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,無形的武器已然到手 LIAR
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.74,0:03:56.92,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,是為了什麼 要守護什麼 才經過漫長等待
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.92,0:04:01.55,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,就用這顆子彈破壞一切！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.55,0:04:06.72,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,NEVER LIE 即使在這僅剩黑白 暗無光輝的世界裡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.72,0:04:11.64,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,NEVER END NEVER LIE 心靈絕不沾染黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.64,0:04:17.48,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,THE END OF WORLD 在絕望中握住僅存的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.48,0:04:26.40,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,用顫抖的手指瞄準目標 去追尋未來！
Comment: 0,0:22:26.19,0:22:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,——————————————EDJP——————————————
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.04,0:21:58.26,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}終わりが始まるアリアと共に
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.26,0:22:02.93,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}白旗を掲げた奇跡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.43,0:22:08.68,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}脱獄の果てに歓声の中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.68,0:22:12.85,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}手錠突き付けられ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.31,0:22:18.73,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}ほら、見て　愚かな駒よ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.73,0:22:23.78,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}断罪の茶番
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.86,0:22:26.53,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}独壇場Funky
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.53,0:22:29.20,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}その目で見ろ　競争
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.25,0:22:34.29,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}{\fad(200,200)}Forget
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.20,0:22:34.29,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}欺いてよ　Close Enough
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.29,0:22:36.88,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}多発的な展開
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.88,0:22:39.67,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}人の波を掻き分け
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.67,0:22:42.38,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}叫べ　My Justice，Right Way
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.38,0:22:44.76,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Make it a vow!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.76,0:22:47.39,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}感心できるのはFunky
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.39,0:22:50.10,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}喪失だけが拒止
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.10,0:22:55.10,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}導いてよ　Close Enough
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.15,0:22:57.77,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}鮮烈過ぎた年回
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.86,0:22:59.94,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}偏見のあるカテゴライズ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.94,0:23:02.15,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Don't believe no story
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.15,0:23:04.20,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}I know you're ready
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.20,0:23:06.07,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}No, we're already over
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.07,0:23:08.07,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Everybody loves despair
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.07,0:23:11.49,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}I'll sadly go from the end
Comment: 0,0:21:47.70,0:21:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,——————————————EDCN——————————————
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.04,0:21:58.26,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}伴隨著結尾即開始的詠嘆調
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.26,0:22:02.93,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}高舉白旗的奇蹟
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.43,0:22:08.68,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}在逃獄後的歡呼聲中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.68,0:22:12.85,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}被強行拷上了手銬
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.31,0:22:18.73,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}看吧 愚昧的棋子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.73,0:22:23.78,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這定罪的把戲
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.86,0:22:26.53,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}奇異的獨角戲舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.53,0:22:29.20,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}用你的眼睛看著 競爭
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.25,0:22:34.29,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}{\fad(200,200)}遺落
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.20,0:22:34.29,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}欺騙吧 Close Enough
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.29,0:22:36.88,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}多線並行的發展
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.88,0:22:39.67,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}撥開人群
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.67,0:22:42.38,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}呼喊著 這是我正義的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.38,0:22:44.76,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}許下你的誓言
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.76,0:22:47.39,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}值得讚美的驚恐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.39,0:22:50.10,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}唯獨拒絕喪失
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.10,0:22:55.10,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}指引我吧 Close Enough
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.15,0:22:57.77,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}過於艷麗的忌日
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.86,0:22:59.94,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}帶有偏見的分類
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.94,0:23:02.15,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不要相信沒有故事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.15,0:23:04.20,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我知道你準備好了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.20,0:23:06.07,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不 我們已經結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.07,0:23:08.07,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}人人都愛著絕望
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.07,0:23:11.49,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我會滿懷悲傷地離去
